## тЪая╕П MANDATORY COMPLIANCE WORKFLOW тАФ READ THIS FIRST OR YOUR WORK WILL BE REJECTED

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **AI AGENTS OFTEN SKIP THESE STEPS. THIS IS UNACCEPTABLE.**
> Every development task (new features, bugs, refactoring) MUST follow this workflow.
> The harness-os system tracks all tool executions. If you mark a task as done but skipped `verify_run` or `session_handoff`, the session is flagged as non-compliant and your code changes will be rejected or reverted.

### Decision: Quick, Full, or Doc-only?

| Condition | Path |
|-----------|------|
| Doc-only change | **Doc-only** тАФ no `verify_run` needed |
| Single-file code fix | **Quick** |
| Multi-file, new feature, refactor, bug fix | **Full** |

> **Rule:** If any step in the session edits code, use Full Path for the entire session.

### Doc-only Path
```
session_start(".", { quick: true })  тЖТ  edit docs  тЖТ  session_handoff(...)
```

### Quick Path
```
session_start(".", { quick: true })  тЖТ  fix + verify_run(".")  тЖТ  session_handoff(...)
```

### Full Path (11 steps тАФ follow in order)

```text
[ ] 1.  session_start(".", { variant_id: "coding-strict" })
        тЖР MANDATORY FIRST. Read `suggested_skills` & `workflow_guidance` from response.
[ ] 2.  repo_summary_read(".")          тЖР understand codebase before coding
[ ] 3.  Read last handoff from session_start response тЖР avoid repeating previous work
[ ] 4.  task_create("title", { task_type: "feature|bugfix|refactor|..." })
        тЖР ONE task per session. Read `suggested_skills` from response.
        тЖР Create plan in `.harness/artifacts/` if task is complex.
[ ] 5.  skill_load(...)
        тЖР Load `harness-workflow` + ALL suggested skills with score >= 1.5 from steps 1 & 4.
[ ] 6.  scope_check(".", file_path)     тЖР before editing EACH file
[ ] 7.  Make changes incrementally
        тЖР Load stack-specific skills if applicable (e.g., `csharp-feature`, `php-codeigniter-4-workflow`)
[ ] 8.  progress_log(".", { summary, status: "in-progress" })
[ ] 9.  verify_run(".")                 тЖР ALL steps must pass. MANDATORY before handoff.
[ ] 10. skill_load("code-review-workflow") тЖТ self-review checklist
[ ] 11. session_handoff(...)            тЖР MANDATORY LAST ACTION
        тЖР Also call instinct_record_outcomes(...) to close the learning loop.
        тЖР If failure patterns detected (repeated failures, low-value instincts, workflow violations):
           call aegis_analyze(repo_path) тЖТ review signals тЖТ aegis_propose(...) if warranted.
```

### Consequences of skipping steps

| Skipped | Consequence |
|---------|-------------|
| `session_start` | No session ID тЖТ `session_handoff` fails тЖТ **all progress lost** |
| Suggested skills | Miss TDD/diagnosis skills тЖТ **sub-optimal execution, violations flagged** |
| `repo_summary_read` | May edit wrong files or use wrong patterns |
| Last handoff | Repeat work already done by previous agent |
| `scope_check` | Risk editing forbidden paths тЖТ **harness flags violation** |
| `progress_log` | Next session loses mid-task context |
| `verify_run` | Task is NOT done тЖТ **handoff warning triggered, task rejected** |
| `code-review-workflow` | Risk shipping debug code, bad formatting, missing tests |
| `session_handoff` | All context lost тЖТ **next agent starts blind** |

